metadata.name: Space Bapes Certificate
metadata.description: The Space Bapes Certificate (SBC) works as the one and only VIP Whitelist token for the upcoming Space Bapes collection dropping in October 2022. Holders of the SBC will have premium access for a guaranteed mint on the project, along with the cheapest mint price. Powered by BAPESCLAN, and ChainTech Labs! Join our ecosystem and build your own universe with utility that will TAKE YOU TO OUTER SPACE, and beyond!
